Package com.sportradar.livedata.sdk.proto.common

Interface ProtocolListener<I extends IncomingMessage>

public interface ProtocolListener<I extends IncomingMessage>
Represents a listener used to observe the Protocol implementation

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void onDisconnected()
    Invoked by the observed Protocol instance when the connection to the server is closed due to user request.
    void onLinkEvent​(FeedEventType event, Object data)
    Invoked by the observed Protocol instance when there is an error about which the user has to be notified.
    void onLoggedIn()
    Invoked by the observed Protocol instance when it logs(registers) with the server.
    void onMessageReceived​(I message)
    Invoked by the observed Protocol instance when a message is received from the server.
